🟢 PART 4: JENKINS (CI/CD PIPELINE)
Step 10: Install Jenkins

Open:

http://localhost:8080
Step 11: Create Pipeline Job
New Item → Pipeline → OK
Step 12: Paste Pipeline Code
pipeline {
    agent any

    stages {

        stage('Clone Code') {
            steps {
                git 'https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/ABISHA_AGILE.git'
            }
        }

        stage('Build Docker Image') {
            steps {
                bat 'docker build -t static-app .'
            }
        }

        stage('Run Container') {
            steps {
                bat 'docker run -d -p 8082:80 static-app'
            }
        }

        stage('Deploy to Kubernetes') {
            steps {
                bat 'kubectl apply -f deployment.yaml'
                bat 'kubectl apply -f service.yaml'
            }
        }
    }
}

👉 Click Build Now
👉 See Stage View (important)

